data.eligibility_criteria:
The inclusion criteria of this study were as followed:

1. PTC confirmed by fine-needle aspiration (FNA);
2. Confirmed low-risk mutation types by next-generation sequencing (NGS) before surgery;
3. No severe functional diseases, such as heart failure, severe respiratory diseases, or renal failure;
4

Inclusion Criteria:

1. Age \> 18 years;
2. Patients with end-stage renal disease (ESRD) receiving hemodialysis or peritoneal dialysis treatment \> 3 months prior surgery;
3. Severe secondary hyperparathyroidism defined as iPTH level \> 800 pg/ml, followed with hypercalcemia and/or hyperphosphatemia
